---

## рџ“Ў Kafka Event Flow

| Event | Trigger |
|-------|---------|
| `Order_Created` | New order placed |
| `Order_Updated` | Order details modified |
| `Order_Deleted` | Order removed |

Events are consumed by **Inventory Service** (stock adjustment) and **Notification Service** (email alerts).

---

## рџ”— Inter-Service Communication

- **Inventory Service** вЂ” `GET /check_inventory/{product_id}/{quantity}` is called before order creation to verify stock availability
- **User Service** вЂ” JWT tokens issued by User Service are verified via `authenticate.py`
